Feyerabend&rsquo;s half became his best-known work: <em>Against
Method</em>. Publishes a contemptuous review of Popper&rsquo;s
<em>Objective Knowledge</em>.</td> </tr>
<tr>
  <td>1975</td>
  <td><em>Against Method. Outline of an Anarchistic Theory of
