<h2 id="Oth">Other Internet Resources</h2>

<ul>

 <li><a href="http://www.collodel.org/feyerabend/" target="other">The Works of Paul Feyerabend</a>
 is a complete and regularly updated bibliography of
Feyerabend&rsquo;s works.</li>

 <li><a href="https://www.pkfcentennial.org/">PKF Centennial 2024</a>
 provides links to a wide range of related material (recent
publications, audio and videos, centennial conferences).</li>

 <li><a href="https://www.pkfeyerabend.org/en/paul-k-feyerabend/">Paul K. Feyerabend Foundation</a>
 promotes the empowerment and well-being of disadvantaged human
communities.</li>
